column2: SELECT m.specobjid, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, p.z, n.z as z_photo, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2, p.specobjid AS spec FROM MyDB.gz2_# AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.ObjID = o.ObjID LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS p ON m.specobjid = p.specobjid
